OL,3,CTributes paid to 'formidable
OL,4,Ccharacter' Claire Lomas ahead of
OL,5,Cchurch service
OL,7,FA "formidable character" is how a
OL,8,Ffriend of Leicestershire record-
OL,9,Fbreaker and fundraiser Claire Lomas
OL,10,Fwill remember her, following her death
OL,11,Fafter an accident in the Middle East.
OL,13,FA church service to celebrate her life
OL,14,Fwill take place in Melton Mowbray on
OL,15,FWednesday 2 October. Claire died on
OL,16,FAugust 22, following an accident in
OL,17,FJordan. She was 44-years-old.
OL,19,FShe raised nearly a million pounds for
OL,20,Fcharity after being paralysed in a
OL,21,Fhorse riding accident in 2007.
