OL,7,FShe famously walked the London
OL,8,FMarathon in 2012 wearing a "bionic
OL,9,Fsuit."
OL,11,FMs Lomas was a beneficiary of the Matt
OL,12,FHampson Foundation, which was founded
OL,13,Fby the former England and Leicester
OL,14,FTigers rugby player.
OL,16,FMatt was paralysed from the neck down
OL,17,Fafter a training accident at the age
OL,18,Fof 20.
