OL,7,FPaying tribute to Claire, Matt said:
OL,8,F"She really went out of her way to
OL,9,Fsupport other people and show people
OL,10,Fyou could live a great and fulfilled
OL,11,Flife after a serious injury."
OL,13,F'She was an amazing person to be
OL,14,Faround - she had a great energy and
OL,15,Fzest for life,' Matt Hampson pays
OL,16,Ftribute to Claire Lomas
