OL,7,FSpeaking of their bond, he said: "She
OL,8,Fwanted to live life to the full...she
OL,9,Fwas a formidable character, who led
OL,10,Ffrom the front and was very much a
OL,11,Fleader.
OL,13,F"We could resonate with each other and
OL,14,Funderstand each other from a sporting
OL,15,Fbackground and we understood life was
OL,16,Fnever going to be the same again after
OL,17,Four injuries.
