OL,7,F"But we also understood that life was
OL,8,Fbrilliant and you could go on and
OL,9,Fachieve great things even if it may
OL,10,Fnot have been the path that you
OL,11,Foriginally thought you were going to
OL,12,Fgo on."
OL,14,FMatt described Claire's smile as
OL,15,F"infectious."
OL,17,FHe said she'd want to be remembered as
OL,18,Fsomeone who "wanted to live life her
OL,19,Fway".
